1. Ja ću *okrenuti* kola prema jugu. (I will turn the car towards the south.)
2. Ona je *okrenula* stranicu knjige. (She turned the page of the book.)
3. Moramo *okrenuti* novu stranicu u našem odnosu. (We need to turn a new page in our relationship.)
4. Oni su *okrenuli* glave kada su čuli buku. (They turned their heads when they heard the noise.)
5. Molim vas da *okrenete* broj telefona koji sam vam dao. (Please dial the phone number that I gave you.)
6. On je bio *okrenut* svom poslu i nije primetio da sam ušao u sobu. (He was focused on his work and didn't notice that I entered the room.)
7. *Okreni* se leđima prema meni. (Turn your back towards me.)
8. Ona se često *okreće* prošlosti. (She often looks back to the past.)
9. *Okrenuo* sam se jer sam čuo nešto iza sebe. (I turned around because I heard something behind me.)
10. Molim te, *okreni* taj ključ u bravu. (Please turn the key in the lock.)

Note: The word "okrenuti" in Serbian can have multiple meanings depending on the context, which is reflected in the different translations provided.